flowchart LR
    %%{init: {'theme': 'neutral', "themeVariables": { "fontSize": "16px"}}}%%
    A([User Input: Keypress])

    subgraph Debounce [React Debounce State]
        direction TB
        B(Start Timer)
        C(Input Resets Timer)
        D(1000ms Elapses)
        B -->|Interrupted| C
        B -->|Clean| D
    end

    subgraph Sync [State Reconciliation]
        direction TB
        E(Merge Visual Delta)
        F(HTTP PUT /edit/slide)
        E --> F
    end

    subgraph Server [Go Backend API]
        direction TB
        G(Intercept & Validate JWT)
        H(Persist JSONB to DB)
        G --> H
    end

    I([UI Auto-Saved Alert])

    A --> Debounce
    Debounce --> Sync
    Sync --> Server
    Server --> I
